{"pageProps":{"bookPath":"leetcode","postPath":"lc-paint-house","post":{"title":"【LeetCode】256. 刷房子","body":"<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/paint-house/\">256. 刷房子</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>设 <code>dp[i]</code> 表示把第 <code>i</code> 间房子刷完得到的最小花费，其实从 <code>dp[i]</code> 到 <code>dp[i+1]</code> 的公式是不太好推的，所以换一种思路。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>设 <code>dp[i]</code> 表示把第 <code>i</code> 间房子分别刷成三种颜色的最小花费，那么显然有以下结论：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre>dp[i+1] = [\n    costs[i+1][0] + min(dp[i][1], dp[i][2]),\n    costs[i+1][1] + min(dp[i][0], dp[i][2])\n    costs[i+1][2] + min(dp[i][0], dp[i][1])\n]</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这样，本题的答案就是 <code>min(dp[costs.length-1])</code> 了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>我们注意到这个递推关系里，只关心前一项，所以写代码的时候可以对空间进行些优化。代码如下：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number[][]}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">costs</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> minCost = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">costs</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (costs.length === <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dp = costs[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; costs.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> [f, s, t] = costs[i];\n        dp = [\n            f + <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>], dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]),\n            s + <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>], dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>]),\n            t + <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>], dp[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>])\n        ]\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(...dp)\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>","createTime":1610035200000,"authorName":"weily","type":"adoc"},"book":{"title":"LeetCode","toc":[{"title":"53. 最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-subarray"},{"title":"62. 不同路径","path":"lc-unique-paths"},{"title":"63. 不同路径 II","path":"lc-unique-paths-ii"},{"title":"64. 最小路径和","path":"lc-minimum-path-sum"},{"title":"70. 爬楼梯","path":"lc-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"95. 不同的二叉搜索树 II","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees-ii"},{"title":"96. 不同的二叉搜索树","path":"lc-unique-binary-search-trees"},{"title":"120. 三角形最小路径和","path":"lc-triangle"},{"title":"121. 买卖股票","path":"lc-buy-stock"},{"title":"132. 分割回文串 II","path":"lc-palindrome-partitioning-ii"},{"title":"152. 乘积最大子数组","path":"lc-maximum-product-subarray"},{"title":"198. 打家劫舍","path":"lc-house-robber"},{"title":"256. 粉刷房子","path":"lc-paint-house"},{"title":"276. 栅栏涂色","path":"lc-paint-fence"},{"title":"303. 区域和检索 - 数组不可变","path":"lc-range-sum-query-immutable"},{"title":"746. 使用最小花费爬楼梯","path":"lc-min-cost-climbing-stairs"},{"title":"146. LRU 缓存机制","path":"lc-lru-cache"},{"title":"数完全二叉树节点","path":"lc-count-complete-tree-nodes"}],"path":"leetcode"}},"__N_SSG":true}